-----------------------------

in the environment, we have different variables

$ go env

One of them is GOOS ( or goos )

$ GOOS="windows" go build       : to  build windows executable , automatically finds the main.go file

$ GOOS="darwin" go build        : to build mac executable

$ GOOS="linux" go build         : to build linux executable

-----------------------------

Memory management:  Memory alloc and dealloc happens automatically
                    garb collec. is automatic
                    out of scope becomes nil

new() and make()

new()   : alloc memory but not initialized
        : zeroed storage

make()  : alloc mem and initializes
        : non-zeroed storage

